Bloodystrike shruggs as Skulletron's question. "Energon injections, various 
viruses, mutilation. Nemesis invented a few devices for extreme pain. The 
ussual."

He stops by a door, opening it. "Here it is."

Bloodystrike looks inside the room, noticing that there was alot of mech 
fluid on the floor. "There was a battle in here a little while ago. The place 
still needs to be cleaned up."
